  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to KDesignerPlugin</title>

    <para>
      The <application>KDesignerPlugin</application> package contains plugins for
      Qt Designer that allow it to display the widgets provided by various KDE
      frameworks.
    </para>

    &lfs77_checked;

